<i>adjective</i>: 우스꽝스럽다 [우스꽝스럽따] <i>determiner</i>: 희화적 [히화적], 희극적 [히극쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우스꽝스럽다 [우스꽝스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. ridiculous; laughable; comical</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동, 모습 등이 보통과 달라 우습다.</dd><br>
<dd>Funny because one's remarks, behavior, appearance, etc., are not ordinary.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ludicrous; absurd; nonsensical</dd><br>
<dd>매우 못나서 우스운 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Somewhat funny because something or someone is very foolish.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>희화적 [히화적]</dt><br>
<dd>comical; humorous; witty</dd><br>
<dd>우습고 재미있는.</dd><br>
<dd>Being funny and humorous.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>희극적 [히극쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. comical</dd><br>
<dd>희극의 요소를 가진.</dd><br>
<dd>Having comical elements.</dd><br>
<dd>2. farcical</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동, 모습 등이 우스꽝스러운.</dd><br>
<dd>One's words, action, or appearance being ridiculous.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>